name: Arado Websearch
tag_list: bookmarks, database, rss, url, browser, search, websearch, synchronize
description: Arado Websearch is a Bookmark Database.
overview: Arado Websearch is an open source Bookmark-Database for Websearch. You easily can save and organize your favourite URLs (Bookmarks). So, Arado Websearch is a complete bookmark management solution that will allow you to synchronize, organize, manage, remove duplicates and check your favorite internet pages, if their content has changed. The database can be networked with your further devices like laptop, mobile phone, home or work PC, so that all added URLs are synchronized with your connected devices. The Arado websearch experience provides to search the web within all your networked devices. The app uses c++ and Qt framework around a SQLite Database.
